textAnnotations.description:
LIFE OF A DEMOCRAT
IM NOT FULLY
CHEATING. IT'S
ONLY ORAL SEX!
WHAT A
RELIEF!
THEY DIDN'T LAY
ME OFFI I GOT
DEMOTED TO PART TIME!
DUDE-I CAN
LIVE IN MINI-
STORAGE!
SORRY YOUR
HOUSE BURNED
DOWN
MY CANDIDATE
DIDN'T LOSE
BY VERY MUCH!
I'D SHOOT
HIM, BUT HE'D
LOVE ENDING !
UP IN A COMA
INSTEAD oF
DEAD
8-11-05-B
